    <item>
      <title>Event-Driven Pattern vs Event Sourcing Pattern vs Publisher-Subscriber Pattern vs Producer-Consumer Pattern</title>
      <link>https://buenhyden.github.io/posts/software-design-and-architecture/architectural-patterns/event-driven-pattern-vs-event-sourcing-pattern-vs-publisher-subscriber-pattern-vs-producer-consumer-pattern/</link>
